---
---
<section id="about">
  <span class="comment">// about me</span>
  <div class="grid">
    <p class="bio">
      QA-Profi am Tag, iOS-Entwickler und Homelab-Tinkerer in der Freizeit.
      Ich interessiere mich dafür wie Systeme funktionieren — ob Software,
      Hardware oder Netzwerk.
    </p>
    <div class="facts">
      <span class="facts-label">quick facts</span>
      <ul>
        <li>📍 Deutschland</li>
        <li>🧪 Test Engineer</li>
        <li>📱 iOS Developer</li>
        <li>🖥️ Self-Hoster</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .comment {
    color: var(--text-subdued);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .bio {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .facts {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .facts-label {
    color: var(--accent-green);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  ul { list-style: none; }
  li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 2.1;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
